# Cloudflare Pages redirects file
# https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/
#
# Explicitly force any unmatched route to serve the custom 404 page with a
# real 404 status. Cloudflare Pages normally auto-detects a top-level
# 404.html, but this rule guarantees it regardless of project/runtime
# configuration (classic Pages vs. the newer Workers static-assets model).
/*   /404.html   404
